{"type":"message","id":"1991e025","parentId":"a8c6c82e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:40:22.523Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"上下文使用率已经达到72%，超过了60%的阈值。按照脚本的设计，应该考虑开始一个新会话来重置上下文。\n\n让我检查一下当前 session 的状态，然后根据 AGENTS.md 中的指示，我应该在上下文达到85%之前主动创建新会话。现在是72%，还可以继续使用，但接近阈值了。\n\n我需要查看当前的内存状态和会话信息，以便做出决定。","thinkingSignature":"d8d42e20b46a8d484ee3dfd9bd28879fe62d96f90d7993b8e82066de8e4a2879"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vh86vs0z91t6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw sessions --json","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1395,"output":113,"cacheRead":38931,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40439,"cost":{"input":0.0004185,"output":0.0001356,"cacheRead":0.00116793,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017220299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774075218460}}
